<!--T:1-->
'''Trust Rank''' is part of the [[Special:MyLanguage/Trust and Safety|Trust and Safety]] system in VRChat, designed to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for all users. This system determines when a user can upload content, and evaluates user behavior to calculate "Trust", using an aggregate of many variables.

==Ranks== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:3-->
A user’s Trust feeds into their '''Trust Rank''', an indicator of their time spent in VRChat, content contribution, friendships made, and other factors. 

<!--T:4-->
The ranks they gain are as follows (lowest to highest):
