===Gaining ranks=== <!--T:7-->

<!--T:8-->
The inner workings of the Trust system are intentionally hidden to prevent exploitation.  

<!--T:9-->
However, the best way to raise your Trust Rank is to engage in normal activities in VRChat, such as: 

<!--T:10-->
* Exploring
*Making friends
*Creating content

<!--T:11-->
Activities that will not raise your Trust Rank include: 
*Standing or idling in a room (AFKing).
*Uploading a large amount of low-effort content.
*Mass-friending large numbers of users.
*Harassment towards other VRChat users.
Additionally, subscribing to [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]], or being gifted a VRC+ subscription can increase your Trust Rank<ref>[https://hello.vrchat.com/vrchatplus VRC+] on VRChat's website; retrieved October 24, 2024.</ref>. However it will only increase it once.

<!--T:29-->
However, in some cases, the Trust Rank does not necessarily increase, but it does provide a boost in reaching the next rank.

<!--T:23-->
==Trust ranks and safety ==
[[File:Shield_level.webp|thumb|300px|Shield levels can be customized, depending on a user's Trust Rank.]]
